{"tid":2063912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【公務員要宣誓擁護政權】黃絲公務員要delete FB/IG/連登acc了","createTime":"2020-06-14T11:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T12:45:31.000Z","uid":202464,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ad5618d39ca0225532ad923d0f7822dfceeb49ed","tid":2063912,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T11:34:56.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局局長聶德權早前發表「公務員雙重身份論」引起爭議，他昨日再就言論解畫，指公務員是向特區政府及行政長官負責，而行政長官透過中央任命，故公務員是透過行政長官向中央負責。他又透露，下月將會就公務員的宣誓形式及範圍發表研究報告，預料包括擁護《基本法》及效忠特區政府等。有公務員團體希望政府盡快交代宣誓形式及內容；亦有學者認為應將公務員違反宣誓內容刑事化，以加強阻嚇作用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20200614/mobile/odn-20200614-0614_00176_037.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200614%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20200614-0614_00176_037.html&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=f7ce6c46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20200614/mobile/odn-20200614-0614_00176_037.html</a>"},{"pid":"b42eab6cd365a3018fe1326ea0072421ef1d406d","tid":2063912,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T11:35:55.000Z","msg":"等睇大堆黃絲del fb同ig"},{"pid":"dbc1c9f0acd7938c1559931399b979f8f4ebcd3a","tid":2063912,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T11:49:54.000Z","msg":"公務員前線好黃"},{"pid":"3bf204298820631384c5762c9542c442b044b13f","tid":2063912,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T11:54:03.000Z","msg":"快d delete fb啦"},{"pid":"f403ff22170526945cdbebae9b9c96422b017049","tid":2063912,"uid":52760,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T11:54:16.000Z","msg":"標題黨<br />\n邊句講del fb ig"},{"pid":"aeab7b33c8248376f69ccfd5dc27fc9e6233befd","tid":2063912,"uid":65790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f403ff22170526945cdbebae9b9c96422b017049","tid":2063912,"uid":52760,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTi